{
  "stem": "2684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to mix, because we ate in the same table, because by that time, it was my parents and other adults lived in, in the same bedroom between-- two set of parents lived in one bedroom, and the third set of parents lived in, in the lunchroom, including the children.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they cooked in the kitchen together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I said to you that we were a middle class family before all these things started, we had a bath about three times a week because we had our own bathroom.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In those days, that meant you were rich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had the showers and we had hot water system.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the moving started from our home to a Jewish house, all this stopped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and sometimes I was having not a bath, but having a dish full of water and wash myself and a lady, half naked, one of the mothers, like, she was having a wash next to me in another dish.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the, the the-- the drop of living standard, it's-- it immediately arised.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from then on, I knew I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What my parents did, they still had the shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they still could go to the shop, but they only could go with their stars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the shop was also marked as a Jewish shop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, we couldn't get poultry, because Jews wasn't allowed to sell poultry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were allowed to sell fruit, like apples, and oranges, and fruits.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they opened a fruit shop about 500, 600 meters from the market in a-- in a closed shop, not an open market.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went there every day exactly the same way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I know my father-- now my memory is a little bit came back immediately.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
